<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="hero-card rise-enter">
    <view class="hero-eyebrow">
      <text>IMPORT ASSISTANT</text>
      <text>自动导入</text>
    </view>
    <view class="hero-title">贴一个第三方链接，先自动抓成草稿，再决定要不要入库。</view>
    <view class="hero-subtitle">默认优先走自动解析，识别不完整时再补一点标题或正文，不再要求先整段复制粘贴。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="surface-card section-shell fade-enter">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title-wrap">
        <text class="section-kicker">AUTO IMPORT</text>
        <text class="section-title">链接自动解析</text>
        <text class="section-subtitle">把第三方分享链接贴进来，系统会自动提取标题、简介、封面和可识别的菜谱信息，先进入待审核队列。</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="form-stack">
      <picker range="{{sourcePlatforms}}" range-key="label" value="{{sourcePlatformIndex}}" bindchange="onPlatformChange">
        <view class="picker-box">
          <text class="field-label">来源平台</text>
          <text class="picker-value">{{sourcePlatforms[sourcePlatformIndex].label}}</text>
        </view>
      </picker>

      <view class="field">
        <text class="field-label">第三方链接</text>
        <input class="field-input" placeholder="粘贴小红书、抖音或网页链接" value="{{sourceUrl}}" bindinput="onUrlInput" />
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="submit-grid">
      <button class="primary-btn submit-btn" bindtap="autoImport" disabled="{{autoImporting}}">
        {{autoImporting ? '解析中...' : '自动解析链接'}}
      </button>
      <button class="ghost-btn submit-btn" bindtap="submitImport" disabled="{{submitting}}">
        {{submitting ? '处理中...' : '手动补充创建草稿'}}
      </button>
    </view>

    <view class="feedback-banner import-tip">
      自动解析适合大多数公开分享页；如果平台拦截过严或内容识别不完整，可以继续往下补标题和正文再提交。
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="surface-card section-shell fade-enter">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title-wrap">
        <text class="section-kicker">FALLBACK</text>
        <text class="section-title">识别不完整时补充</text>
        <text class="section-subtitle">这里只在自动解析不够用时再填，能少填就少填。</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="form-stack compact-stack">
      <view class="field">
        <text class="field-label">手动标题</text>
        <input class="field-input" placeholder="自动识别不到标题时再补" value="{{sourceTitle}}" bindinput="onTitleInput" />
      </view>

      <view class="field">
        <text class="field-label">原始内容</text>
        <textarea class="field-textarea large-textarea" placeholder="只在需要时补正文、食材或步骤，系统会继续粗解析。" value="{{rawText}}" bindinput="onRawTextInput"></textarea>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="surface-card section-shell fade-enter">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title-wrap">
        <text class="section-kicker">REVIEW QUEUE</text>
        <text class="section-title">待审核草稿</text>
        <text class="section-subtitle">自动导入和手动补充都会先到这里，审核通过后再进入正式菜谱库。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="ghost-btn action-pill" bindtap="loadDrafts">刷新</view>
    </view>

    <view class="draft-list" wx:if="{{drafts.length > 0}}">
      <view class="draft-card" wx:for="{{drafts}}" wx:key="_id">
        <view class="draft-head">
          <view class="chip-row">
            <text class="chip chip-light">{{item.sourcePlatform}}</text>
            <text class="chip chip-outline">待审核</text>
          </view>
          <text class="draft-time">{{item.createdAt}}</text>
        </view>
        <text class="draft-title">{{item.parsedRecipe.title}}</text>
        <text class="draft-desc">{{item.parsedRecipe.description}}</text>
        <view class="draft-meta">
          <text class="meta-pill">{{item.categoryLabel}}</text>
          <text class="meta-pill">{{item.difficultyLabel}}</text>
          <text class="meta-pill">{{item.cookingTimeLabel}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="draft-preview">
          <text class="preview-label">{{item.imageCountLabel}}</text>
          <text class="preview-label">{{item.ingredientCountLabel}}</text>
          <text class="preview-label">{{item.stepCountLabel}}</text>
        </view>
        <text class="draft-ocr" wx:if="{{item.ocrPreview}}">{{item.ocrPreview}}</text>
        <text class="draft-ocr draft-ocr-diagnostics" wx:if="{{item.ocrDiagnosticsLabel}}">{{item.ocrDiagnosticsLabel}}</text>
        <view class="draft-actions">
          <view class="ghost-btn mini-btn" wx:if="{{item.sourceImages && item.sourceImages.length}}" bindtap="runDraftOcr" data-id="{{item._id}}">?? OCR</view>
          <view class="ghost-btn mini-btn" bindtap="copyDraftText" data-text="{{item.originalText}}">????</view>
          <view class="danger-btn mini-btn" bindtap="rejectDraft" data-id="{{item._id}}">??</view>
          <view class="primary-btn mini-btn" bindtap="approveDraft" data-id="{{item._id}}">?????</view>
        </view>      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="empty-panel" wx:else>
      <text class="empty-title">{{loadingDrafts ? '正在加载草稿...' : '还没有待审核草稿'}}</text>
      <text class="empty-desc">先贴一个第三方链接试试，自动解析成功后这里就会出现对应草稿。</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
